hu.mag.db

Class TableInfoPlus

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.mag.db.TableInfoPlus

  • public class TableInfoPlus
extends Object
    Additional, mainly data dependent information about tables. Usage: create descendant and overwrite the proper method. Not overwritten methods don't influence the system. (They return with 'null')
    Author:
    MaG
